%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20AI-powered%20robot%20is%20helping%20install%20Amazon's%20largest%20solar%20farm%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robot%20on%20wheels%20lifts%20a%20solar%20panel.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a921defb6d32635ee4feed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223096%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAES%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAES%20Corporation%20introduces%20Maximo%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20robot%20that%20installs%20solar%20panels.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20company%20said%20Maximo%20will%20help%20speed%20up%20renewable%20energy%20transition%20and%20wouldn't%20replace%20humans.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBig%20tech%20companies%20need%20more%20renewable%20energy%2C%20and%20fast%2C%20to%20power%20their%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EInstalling%20solar%20panels%20can%20be%20back-breaking%20work%2C%20so%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20renewable%20energy%20companies%20is%20using%20robots%20to%20do%20the%20heavy%20lifting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAES%20Corporation%20on%20Tuesday%20introduced%20%26quot%3BMaximo%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20AI-powered%20robot%20that%20can%20lift%20solar%20panels%20and%20precisely%20place%20them%20into%20long%20rows.%20The%20robot%20will%20be%20used%20to%20construct%20the%20largest%20solar%20farm%20with%20battery%20storage%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20will%20help%20power%20Amazon's%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20really%20focused%20on%20speed%2C%26quot%3B%20Chris%20Shelton%2C%20AES'%20chief%20product%20officer%2C%20said%20during%20a%20call%20with%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20by%20speed%2C%20we%20mean%20speed%20for%20the%20customers%20%E2%80%94%20so%20getting%20these%20projects%20online%20faster%20%E2%80%94and%20speed%20for%20the%20energy%20transition.%20The%20more%20%5Bsolar%5D%20we%20can%20deploy%2C%20the%20more%20we%20can%20reduce%20overall%20carbon%20in%20the%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAES%20said%20Maximo%20can%20install%20solar%20panels%20twice%20as%20fast%20as%20humans%20and%20at%20half%20the%20cost.%20The%20robot%20was%20tested%20in%20various%20outdoor%20conditions%20at%20projects%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Virginia%2C%20Ohio%2C%20and%20Louisiana%20and%20has%20installed%20about%2010%20megawatts%20of%20energy%20to%20date.%20Amazon's%20solar%20farm%20in%20Kern%20County%2C%20California%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20have%20200%20times%20that%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20automation%20comes%20as%20analysts%20predict%20there%20won't%20be%20enough%20workers%20to%20keep%20pace%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsolar-careers-in-demand-workforce-shortage-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20rapid%20rise%20in%20solar%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20pouring%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20into%20renewable%20energy%20under%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20administration%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Feere%2Fsolar%2Fsolar-workforce-development%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAccording%2520to%2520the%2520Solar%2520Futures%2Cand%25201%252C500%252C000%2520workers%2520by%25202035.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforecasted%20that%20the%20solar%20workforce%3C%2Fa%3E%20needed%20to%20at%20least%20double%20to%20500%2C000%20workers%20by%202035%20to%20reach%20a%20national%20goal%20of%20100%25%20carbon-free%20electricity%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20and%20other%20big%20tech%20companies%20are%20driving%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20demand%20for%20renewable%20energy.%20They%20have%20ambitious%20climate%20goals%2C%20yet%20are%20building%20out%20power-hungry%20data%20centers%20to%20store%20our%20data%20and%20develop%20AI.%20In%20some%20states%2C%20those%20power%20demands%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-energy-demand-utilities-green-renewable-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eare%20delaying%20the%20closure%20of%20dirty%20power%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuickly%20scaling%20up%20solar%20farms%20and%20battery%20storage%20is%20key%20to%20keeping%20corporate%20climate%20promises.%20But%20adding%20Maximo%20to%20solar%20sites%20could%20also%20fuel%20concerns%20that%20robots%20will%20dim%20human%20job%20prospects%2C%20just%20as%20automation%20replaced%20some%20factory%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERon%20Rodrique%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20project%20management%20at%20AES%20Clean%20Energy%2C%20said%20Maximo%20isn't%20replacing%20human%20solar%20installers%20at%20the%20company's%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaximo%20is%20not%20out%20there%20to%20replace%20the%20panel%20installers%20or%20other%20people%20that%20we%20have%20on%20our%20sites%2C%26quot%3B%20Rodrique%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20really%20about%20that%20safety%20aspect%20of%20taking%20away%20some%20of%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20that%20people%20have%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robot%20places%20a%20solar%20panel%20on%20a%20long%20row.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a932a61a227600e632dc64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224320%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAES%20Corporation%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELifting%2060-pound%20solar%20panels%20repeatedly%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20200%20panels%20a%20day%2C%20in%20desert%20heat%20takes%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20body.%20If%20that%20isn't%20a%20requirement%20of%20the%20job%2C%20Rodrique%20said%20a%20broader%20range%20of%20workers%20could%20apply%2C%20including%20people%20with%20disabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAES%20said%20Maximo%20has%20one%20person%20driving%20the%20robot%20while%20another%20monitors%20and%20controls%20its%20movements%20with%20a%20single%20button%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20with%20Amazon%20is%20just%20the%20beginning.%20If%20all%20goes%20well%2C%20AES%20expects%20Maximo%20to%20help%20clear%20a%20huge%20backlog%20of%20solar%20projects%20over%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20with%20the%20largest%20customers%20being%20data%20center%20hyperscalers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-robots-amazon-solar-farm-aes-maximo-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722418202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a932cefb6d32635ee505d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-robots-amazon-solar-farm-aes-maximo-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AES%20Corporation's%20robot%20can%20lift%20solar%20panels%20and%20precisely%20place%20them%20into%20long%20rows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cboudreau%40insider.com%20(Catherine%20Boudreau)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-robots-amazon-solar-farm-aes-maximo-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Starbucks%20just%20reinvented%20the%20way%20it%20runs%20its%20caf%C3%A9s%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starbucks%20barista%20handing%20over%20a%20coffee%20order%20with%20a%20smiley%20face%20drawn%20on%20the%20cup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a41117a0fc5856d597ef4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20know%20that%20shaky%2C%20nauseated%20feeling%20you%20get%20when%20you've%20had%20too%20much%20coffee%3F%20That's%20how%20Starbucks%20itself%20is%20feeling%20these%20days.%20At%20peak%20hours%2C%20its%20ubiquitous%20caf%C3%A9s%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-menu-drink-order-why-coffee-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eovercrowded%20and%20slow%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Garbled%20names%20written%20in%20Sharpie%20have%20been%20replaced%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsigns-starbucks-order-will-be-messed-up-former-barista-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecomputer-printed%20stickers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20online-ordering%20overachievers%2C%20who%20are%20allowed%20to%20jump%20the%20line.%20Employees%20%E2%80%94%20once%20among%20the%20happiest%20in%20America%20%E2%80%94%20are%20unionizing.%20There's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-bundling-breakfast-combo-deals-sandwich-croissant-tea-coffee-meal-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Enew%20competition%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Dutch%20Bros%20and%20boba%20tea.%20The%20company%20reported%20yesterday%20that%20US%20sales%20have%20dipped%20for%20the%20last%20two%20quarters%2C%20down%202%25%20since%20April%2C%20and%20profits%20are%20off%207.5%25.%20With%20more%20than%2033%2C000%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20coffee%20chain%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20total%20grind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20Starbucks%20seems%20to%20have%20woken%20up%20and%20smelled%20the%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20you%20know.%20On%20July%202%2C%20the%20company%20announced%20a%20major%20revamp%20of%20the%20way%20its%20caf%C3%A9s%20are%20organized.%20Called%20the%20%26quot%3BSiren%20Craft%20System%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20overhauls%20the%20workflow%20at%20some%2010%2C000%20of%20its%20coffeehouses%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20reduce%20inefficiency%2C%20speed%20up%20orders%2C%20and%20boost%20customer%20satisfaction.%20But%20unlike%20most%20plans%20dreamed%20up%20by%20fancy-pants%20consultants%2C%20Siren%20Craft%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Edoesn't%20try%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-siren-system-will-cut-lines-shorten-wait-rollout-slow-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecranking%20up%20the%20assembly%20line%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20flogging%20employees%20into%20a%20state%20of%20heightened%20productivity.%20Instead%2C%20it%20does%20something%20truly%20novel%20in%20American%20business%3A%20It%20attempts%20to%20actually%20fix%20what's%20wrong%20with%20pretty%20much%20every%20company%20that%20makes%20things%20for%20lots%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20fast-food%20outlet%2C%20Starbucks%20caf%C3%A9s%20included%2C%20is%20a%20little%20factory.%20The%20order%20of%20operations%20is%20highly%20prescribed%2C%20a%20carefully%20choreographed%20system%20of%20specialization%20that's%20been%20timed%20down%20to%20the%20second.%20For%20Starbucks%2C%20the%20trick%20is%20to%20balance%20America's%20addiction%20to%20cheap%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Espeedy%20service%20with%20the%20vibe%20of%20a%20European-style%20coffeeshop%20%E2%80%94%20creating%20a%20relaxed%2C%20enjoyable%20%26quot%3Bthird%20place%26quot%3B%20for%20people%20to%20hang%20out%20beyond%20their%20office%20and%20home.%20There's%20a%20reason%20Starbucks%20used%20to%20sell%20CDs%20of%20the%20inoffensively%20groovy%20music%20it%20played%20in%20its%20caf%C3%A9s.%20People%2C%20it%20understood%2C%20need%20a%20cozy%20place%20to%20doomscroll.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Siren%20Craft%20System%20tries%20to%20get%20this%20recipe%20right.%20For%20starters%2C%20it%20changes%20the%20sequence%20in%20which%20baristas%20make%20drinks.%20That's%20because%20over%20the%20years%2C%20as%20Starbucks%20introduced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-redesigning-stores-cold-drinks-after-recent-success-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Emore%20and%20more%20cold%20beverages%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Frozen%20Strawberry%20A%C3%A7a%C3%AD%20Lemonade%20Refresher%2C%20anyone%3F%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20gotten%20harder%20and%20harder%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20all%20the%20orders.%20%26quot%3BThe%20build%20for%20the%20drinks%20themselves%20have%20gotten%20more%20complex%20and%20has%20more%20steps%2C%20so%20they%20take%20longer%20to%20make%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Michelle%20Eisen%2C%20a%20Starbucks%20barista%20and%20union%20organizer.%20%26quot%3BThe%20order%20in%20which%20we%20were%20asked%20to%20build%20those%20drinks%20was%20no%20longer%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20system%20instructs%20baristas%20to%20push%20cold%20drinks%20down%20in%20the%20queue%20in%20favor%20of%20hot%20ones.%20That%20might%20seem%20surprising%2C%20given%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20milkshake-like%20Frappuccino%20line%20and%20the%20fruity%20Refreshers.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%2C%20the%20cold%20drinks%20also%20take%20longer%20to%20make.%20Order%20one%20of%20each%2C%20and%20you'll%20end%20up%20holding%20a%20melting%20Frappuccino%20before%20they%20even%20start%20on%20your%20double%20espresso.%20The%20higher-grossing%20cold%20drinks%20take%20so%20long%20to%20make%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20that%20they're%20actually%20pretty%20low-margin.%20The%20highest-margin%20item%20on%20the%20menu%2C%20a%20person%20familiar%20with%20Starbucks%20operations%20tells%20me%2C%20is%20probably%20a%20plain%20old%20drip%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESiren%20Craft%20also%20switches%20up%20the%20way%20baristas%20make%20coffee.%20They%20used%20to%20pull%20espresso%20shots%20first%20and%20steam%20milk%20second.%20But%20employees%20told%20management%20that%20the%20%3Cem%3Ecaff%C3%A8%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20getting%20cold%20waiting%20for%20the%20%3Cem%3Elatte%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20new%20system%20reverses%20that%20order%20to%20get%20the%20ingredients%20into%20better%20sync.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20digital%20dashboard%20that%20tells%20baristas%20what%20to%20do%20next.%20Starbucks%20is%20about%20to%20expand%20who%20can%20place%20orders%20via%20its%20app%2C%20and%20it's%20expecting%20a%20huge%20influx.%20So%20it's%20reprogramming%20the%20dashboard%20to%20anticipate%20when%20a%20flood%20of%20orders%20is%20coming%20and%20warn%20supervisors%2C%20to%20help%20them%20figure%20out%20who%20needs%20to%20be%20doing%20what.%20That%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20minor%20change%2C%20but%20when%20you're%20operating%20at%20the%20scale%20of%20Starbucks%2C%20all%20the%20savings%20in%20seconds%20really%20add%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20in%20perhaps%20its%20biggest%20innovation%2C%20the%20new%20system%20is%20changing%20the%20role%20of%20each%20caf%C3%A9's%20%26quot%3Bpeak%20play%20caller.%26quot%3B%20During%20crunch%20times%2C%20these%20managers%20will%20be%20empowered%20to%20deviate%20from%20everyone's%20set%20assignments%2C%20like%20a%20coach%20calling%20a%20play%20from%20the%20sideline.%20They'll%20be%20able%20to%20move%20employees%20around%2C%20taking%20someone%20off%20the%20espresso%20machine%2C%20say%2C%20and%20putting%20them%20on%20a%20register.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20efficiency%20and%20productivity%20by%20giving%20managers%20more%20flexibility%20to%20improvise%2C%20rather%20than%20by%20throwing%20more%20bodies%20at%20the%20problem.%20Which%20is%20a%20pretty%20profound%20departure%20from%20the%20stopwatch-driven%2C%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%20that%20corporate%20America%20has%20long%20applied%20to%20the%20factory%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20most%20interesting%20about%20Siren%20Craft%2C%20though%2C%20is%20what%20it%20%3Cem%3Eisn't%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It's%20not%20a%20widgetized%20assembly%20line%20that%20doubles%20down%20on%20barista%20performance%20metrics.%20It%20doesn't%20force%20every%20customer%20to%20order%20via%20the%20app%2C%20or%20make%20hand-wavey%20gestures%20at%20AI%20or%20some%20other%20flashy%20approach%20to%20efficiency%20and%20productivity.%20That%20kind%20of%20thinking%20is%20what%20got%20the%20company%20into%20so%20much%20trouble%20in%20the%20first%20place%20%E2%80%94%20poring%20over%20spreadsheets%20rather%20than%20improving%20coffee%20pour-overs.%20Starbucks%20was%20always%20commodified%2C%20but%20it%20went%20so%20far%20in%20that%20direction%20that%20it%20started%20breaking%20the%20brand.%20From%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-acquires-spirit-aerosystems-multi-billion-stock-deal-report-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EBoeing%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-admits-defeat-cookie-plan-relief-could-be-short-lived-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGoogle%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flatest-wells-fargo-news-hirings-layoffs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWells%20Fargo%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20metrics-driven%20pushes%20for%20efficiency%20and%20productivity%20always%20jeopardize%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20product%2C%20alienate%20employees%2C%20and%20drive%20away%20loyal%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20work-from-home%20world%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20Starbucks%20ever%20having%20the%20cachet%20and%20daily%20urgency%20it%20once%20did.%20Fewer%20people%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20warm%20drink%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20office%20or%20a%20post-lunch%20pick-me-up%20%E2%80%94%20and%20given%20rising%20prices%2C%20not%20many%20of%20us%20have%20the%20extra%20%245%20to%20burn.%20But%20it's%20not%20impossible%20for%20the%20company%20to%20bounce%20back.%20A%20visit%20to%20a%20Starbucks%20could%20still%20be%20a%20semi-regular%20treat%2C%20if%20people%20can%20feel%20assured%20that%20their%20quick%20pop-in%20for%20a%20hot%20cup%20of%20joe%20won't%20turn%20into%2025%20minutes%20of%20queuing%20behind%20a%20bunch%20of%20kids%20eager%20for%20a%20frothy%20cold%20sugar%20blast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEisen%20knows%20the%20Siren%20Call%20System%20won't%20employ%20more%20baristas%2C%20as%20the%20union%20would%20like.%20But%20she's%20hopeful%20that%20it%20represents%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction.%20Long%20lines%2C%20after%20all%2C%20don't%20just%20frustrate%20customers.%20They%20also%20prevent%20employees%20from%20serving%20up%20coffee%20with%20a%20more%20human%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20used%20to%20be%20an%20element%20of%20fun%20to%20being%20a%20Starbucks%20barista%2C%26quot%3B%20Eisen%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20amazing%20to%20have%20the%20time%20to%20talk%20to%20customers%20and%20sample%20new%20products%20with%20them%2C%20and%20get%20to%20know%20what%20their%20tastes%20were.%20Anything%20we%20can%20do%20to%20bring%20that%20third-place%20atmosphere%20back%20into%20the%20stores%20would%20be%20nice%20to%20see.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fadam-rogers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAdam%20Rogers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-reinvented-cafes-managment-plan-lines-waits-sales-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722418022000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a411171a227600e632244b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-reinvented-cafes-managment-plan-lines-waits-sales-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20world's%20largest%20coffeehouse%20chain%20is%20struggling.%20Can%20Starbucks%20find%20a%20way%20to%20make%20coffee%20fun%20again%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arogers%40businessinsider.com%20(Adam%20Rogers)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-reinvented-cafes-managment-plan-lines-waits-sales-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Satya%20Nadella%20created%20a%20'learn-it-all'%20culture%20at%20Microsoft%20to%20help%20it%20become%20a%20%243%20trillion%20powerhouse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Microsoft%20CEO%20Satya%20