20was%20gone.%20I%20felt%20humiliated.%20I%20didn't%20report%20it%20to%20the%20police.%20I'd%20heard%20this%20crime%20was%20so%20rife%20that%20they%20were%20unlikely%20to%20be%20able%20to%20do%20anything.%20My%20friend%20got%20us%20an%20Uber%20home%3B%20I%20passed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20I%20found%20out%20just%20how%20much%20he'd%20violated%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20fired%20up%20my%20laptop.%20To%20my%20alarm%2C%20the%20thief%20had%20hacked%20into%20my%20Google%20account%20and%20changed%20the%20password%2C%20locking%20me%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20never%20imagined%20a%20thief%20would%20rob%20my%20phone%20%3Cem%3Eand%3C%2Fem%3E%20hack%20my%20Google.%20I%20suspect%20he%20had%20experience%20doing%20this%20because%20he'd%20changed%20the%20phone's%20password%20before%20it%20could%20lock%20while%20Google%20was%20still%20open%20via%20the%20translator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20received%20a%20panicked%20call%20from%20my%20flatmate%20back%20home%20in%20Sydney.%20The%20thief%20had%20tried%20to%20remove%20all%20the%20money%20from%20a%20joint%20account%20with%20which%20we%20pay%20the%20mortgage.%20Luckily%2C%20he%20was%20unsuccessful.%20I've%20now%20triple-checked%20that%20I%20have%20Face%20ID%20set%20up%20for%20all%20my%20banking%20apps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20a%20new%20smartphone%20the%20day%20after%20the%20theft%3B%20you%20can't%20survive%20more%20than%2024%20hours%20world%20without%20one.%20At%20the%20Apple%20store%20in%20S%C3%A3o%20Paulo%2C%20the%20staff%20said%20they%20often%20saw%20people%20buying%20phones%20because%20their%20previous%20one%20was%20stolen%20the%20day%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20get%20back%20into%20Google%2C%20but%20when%20that%20didn't%20work%2C%20decided%20to%20wait%20a%20few%20days%20before%20trying%20again.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20I%20changed%20every%20account%20linked%20to%20Google%2C%20from%20Spotify%20to%20Skype%2C%20on%20the%20new%20phone.%20I%20battled%20bad%20reception%2C%20endles