0Google%20Authenticator.%20As%20I%20entered%20the%20%26quot%3Bbargaining%26quot%3B%20phase%20of%20grief%20for%20my%20digital%20life%2C%20I%20logged%20out%20and%20back%20on%20again%20to%20ask%20another%20agent.%20They%20told%20me%20to%20try%20again%20from%20a%20familiar%20device%2C%20location%2C%20and%20internet%20connection%20once%20I%20was%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20cycled%20through%20the%20stages%20of%20grief%20%E2%80%94%20denial%2C%20bargaining%2C%20anger%2C%20depression%2C%20and%20acceptance%20%E2%80%94%20over%20the%20next%20two%20weeks.%20For%20two%20days%2C%20I%20barely%20slept%20because%20of%20the%20stress.%20At%20first%2C%20I%20stayed%20in%20the%20apartment.%20Only%20the%20Pride%20event%20tempted%20me%20back%20out%3B%20even%20then%2C%20I%20was%20extra%20cautious%20and%20alert.%20The%20new%20phone%20stayed%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20to%20go%20through%20bank%20statements%20to%20contact%20airline%20companies%20to%20resend%20my%20tickets%20and%20itineraries.%20Whenever%20I%20thought%20I'd%20done%20all%20the%20admin%2C%20another%20nightmare%20popped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20later%2C%20I'm%20still%20locked%20out%2C%20with%20scant%20hope%20of%20ever%20getting%20back%20in.%20My%20former%20employer%20has%20re-fired%20up%20my%20old%20email%20three%20times.%20Each%20time%2C%20Google%20has%20said%20it%20cannot%20verify%20the%20account%20belongs%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20lost%20access%20to%20my%20Gmail%2C%20Google%20Docs%2C%20and%20contacts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%2015%20years%20of%20connections%20and%20all%20the%20essential%20information%20in%20emails%20%E2%80%94%20pitches%2C%20stories%2C%20data%20%E2%80%94%20all%20gone.%20I%20did%20all%20my%20work%20on%20Google%20Docs.%20There%20was%20no%20backup%3B%20Google%20was%20the%20backup.%20I%20have%20lost%20every%20piece%20of%20work%20I've%20written%20for%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20including%20the%20book%20proposal%20that%20took%20four%20months%20to%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20try%20to%20b