t%20Russia's%20Su-57s%20%26quot%3Bare%20the%20high-quality%20assets%2C%20high%20expensive%20assets%2C%20stealth%20fighters%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20want%20to%20lose%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20have%20also%20pointed%20to%20Russian%20fears%20that%20if%20its%20most%20advanced%20jets%20were%20shot%20down%20over%20Ukraine-held%20territory%2C%20it%20would%20expose%20their%20most%20advanced%20technology%20and%20could%20be%20a%20windfall%20for%20Ukraine's%20Western%20partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobinson%20said%20that%20if%20any%20Su-57s%20are%20shot%20down%20over%20Ukrainian-held%20territory%2C%20Western%20intelligence%20experts%20would%20get%26quot%3B%20to%20crawl%20all%20over%20it%20and%20find%20out%20its%20secret.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227687%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20looks%20up%20while%20sitting%20in%20an%20F-16%20fighter%20jet%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6595b1a61c5c7b8c9a0db17b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20sits%20in%20an%20F-16%20fighter%20jet.%3Cp%3EMads%20Claus%20Rasmussen%2FRitzau%20Scanpix%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBaum%20said%20Russia's%20decisions%20on%20what%20goes%20into%20Ukraine%20and%20what%20doesn't%20may%20be%20%26quot%3Bcalculated.%26quot%3B%20They%20may%20have%20decided%20%26quot%3Bthat%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20roll%20out%20their%20more%20sophisticated%20weapons%20yet%20or%20ramp%20up%20their%20sortie%20rate%20yet%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurtis%20said%20that%20Russia%20is%20%26quot%3Bhappy%20to%20lose%20what%20it's%20using%20in%20Ukraine.%20And%20in%20most%20instances%2C%20I'm%20afraid%2C%20that's%20people.%26quot%3B%20Russia%20has%20been%20known%20for%20treating%20its%20soldiers%20as%20disposable%2C%20including%20by%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F