r%2C%20one%20drawback%20for%20Urban%20Revivo%20was%20the%20range%20of%20sizes%20available%20in%20the%20store.%20The%20largest%20jeans%20size%20I%20saw%20was%20a%20US%20size%208%2C%20whereas%2C%20in%20Zara%2C%20the%20range%20went%20up%20to%20size%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20Urban%20Revivo's%20pieces%20were%20more%20street-style%20than%20Zara's.%20Most%20pieces%20had%20a%20neutral%20color%20scheme%20compared%20to%20Zara's%20more%20colorful%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22373b5067-cb9a-40b6-a406-858acacfd69c%5C%22%3EThe%20Urban%20Revivo%20store%20experience%20rivals%20Zara%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20stores%20have%20similar%20aesthetics%2C%20with%20clean%20white%20interiors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZara's%20store%20was%20largely%20open%20concept%20%E2%80%94%20a%20rectangular-shaped%20floor%20plan%20with%20most%20products%20hugging%20the%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22(Composite%20image)%20Zara's%20storefront%20in%20Singapore's%20Jewel%2C%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20its%20interior.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a8b414aab37011780b8ba8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZara's%20storefront%20in%20Singapore's%20Jewel%2C%20and%20a%20picture%20of%20its%20interior.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20very%20brightly%20lit.%20The%20store%20design%20worked%20fine%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%20anything%20spectacular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20Urban%20Revivo%20felt%20like%20it%20had%20intentionally%20curated%20its%20space%20with%20a%20flow%20in%20mind.%20The%20products%20were%20displayed%20in%20aisles%2C%20prompting%20shoppers%20to%20follow%20a%20proposed%20pathway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20store%20also%20had%20arches%2C%20adding%20visual%20interest%20to%20the%20outlet's%20design.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221083%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Urban%20Revivo's%20interior.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a9a181aab37011780be208%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22813%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUrban%20Revivo's%20interior.%3Cp%3EAditi%20Bharade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Zara's%20bright%20lights%2C%20Urban%20Revivo%20was%20lit%20more%20dimly%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20relaxed%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EM%C3%A1rio%20Braz%20de%20Matos%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Flying%20Fish%20Lab%2C%20a%20branding%20consultancy%20agency%20in%20Singapore%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20Urban%20Revivo%20invests%20%26quot%3Bfar%20more%20than%20any%20other%20fast%20fashion%20brand%20in%20the%20shopping%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20something%20other%20brands%20like%20Zara%2C%20H%26amp%3BM%20and%20Uniqlo%20are%20focusing%20less%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4618bb1-1337-41b5-8074-989376f78d2a%5C%22%3EBut%20Zara%20doesn't%20have%20to%20worry%20just%20yet%2C%20experts%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20thought%20that%20Urban%20Revivo%20was%20a%20strong%20alternative%20to%20Zara%2C%20experts%20told%20BI%20it%20doesn't%20pose%20a%20major%20threat%20yet.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20one%2C%20they%20say%20the%20two%20brands%20cater%20to%20different%20target%20demographics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20UR%20(Urban%20Revivo)%20styles%20are%20mostly%20cute%20and%20youthful%2C%20while%20Zara%20offers%20more%20sophisticated%20clothing%2C%20most%20likely%20for%20working%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marcie%20Cooperman%2C%20a%20professor%20from%20the%20fashion%20marketing%20department%20of%20Parsons%20School%20of%20Design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGregory%20Angel%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20fashion%20at%20Parsons%2C%20echoed%20Cooperman's%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUrban%20Revivo%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20products%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20'sophomoric'%20feel%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Angel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20one%20might%20think%20the%20Gaza%20boycott%20would%20have%20people%20searching%20for%20a%20Zara%20alternative%2C%20the%20experts%20are%20skeptical%20that%20political%20activism%20will%20have%20a%20lasting%20impact%20on%20the%20Spanish%20brand's%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCustomers%20do%20not%20have%20the%20courage%20of%20their%20convictions%20for%20very%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooperman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20even%20have%20a%20conviction%20to%20boycott%20a%20brand%2C%20they%20will%20forget%20about%20it%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20see%20something%20cute%20on%20its%20website%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20say%20that%20it's%20too%20early%20to%20determine%20if%20Urban%20Revivo%20will%20be%20a%20true%20threat%20to%20Zara.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFighting%20the%20incumbents%20is%20always%20an%20uphill%20battle%2C%26quot%3B%20Braz%20de%20Matos%20of%20Flying%20Fish%20Lab%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20now%2C%20Urban%20Revivo%20is%20too%20small%20outside%20China%20to%20be%20felt%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20Zara.%20They%20can%20compete%20with%20Zara%20in%20every%20market%20where%20they%20are%20present%20but%20may%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20menace%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAngel%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWill%20it%20be%20a%20competitor%20or%20a%20little%20sister%3F%20The%20market%20has%20yet%20to%20find%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Tang%2C%20CEO%20of%20international%20business%20at%20Fashion%20Momentum%20Group%2C%20Urban%20Revivo's%20parent%20company%2C%20said%20that%20his%20firm%20did%20identify%20Zara%20as%20a%20primary%20competitor.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETang%20added%20that%20while%20both%20companies%20have%20a%20broad%20consumer%20base%2C%20Urban%20Revivo%20is%20gunning%20for%20customers%20who%20are%20%26quot%3Bquality-driven%20elites%2C%20white-collar%20professionals%2C%20and%20the%20new%20generation%20of%20fashion%20pioneers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUrban%20Revivo%20has%20evolved%2C%20particularly%20with%20its%20global%20expansion%2C%20into%20its%20own%20distinct%20market%20position%2C%20despite%20price%20and%20product%20range%20similarities%20to%20Zara%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20strategy%20is%20not%20only%20about%20competing%20with%20Zara%20but%20also%20about%20creating%20a%20distinct%20brand%20image%20and%20influence%20in%20the%20foreign%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20Tang%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Zara%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furban-revivo-convert-but-experts-say-zara-shouldnt-worry-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722415032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a9a1b9aab37011780be20f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furban-revivo-convert-but-experts-say-zara-shouldnt-worry-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Urban%20Revivo%20has%20been%20touted%20as%20Zara's%20rival%20in%20Asia%20and%20is%20looking%20to%20expand%20to%20the%20West.%20BI%20tested%20both%20brands%20to%20see%20which%20provides%20better%20value.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abharade%40insider.com%20(Aditi%20Bharade)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furban-revivo-convert-but-experts-say-zara-shouldnt-worry-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Given%20Early%20Warning%20About%20Landslides%2C%20Potential%20Deaths%3A%20Amit%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKerala%20government%20was%20given%20early%20warning%20on%20July%2023%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20in%20parliament%20on%20Wayanad%20landslides%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722414960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ff9sg27bg_wayanad-landslides-pti_625x300_31_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22