sted%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20the%20building%20owner%20and%20the%20proprietor%20of%20the%20coaching%20centre.%20The%20arrested%20include%20the%20driver%20of%20a%20car%20that%20sped%20through%20the%20flooded%20street%2C%20sending%20a%20wave%20of%20rainwater%20into%20the%20basement.%20That%20arrest%20was%20questioned%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20were%20also%20warned%20that%20failure%20to%20properly%20investigate%20would%20prompt%20the%20court%20to%20transfer%20the%20case%20to%20a%20central%20agency.%C2%A0The%20hearing%20was%20then%20adjourned%20to%202.30%20pm%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETania%20Soni%2C%20Shreya%20Yadav%20-%20both%2025%20-%20and%20Navin%20Delvin%2C%2028%20-%20drowned%20last%20week%20in%20the%20flooded%20basement%20of%20a%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Rajendra%20Nagar.%20Preliminary%20inquiries%20into%20the%20tragedy%20have%20unearthed%20multiple%20violations%20by%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20building%20and%20coaching%20centre%2C%20including%20using%20the%20basement%20without%20due%20clearance%20and%20lying%20to%20obtain%20a%20certificate%20from%20the%20Fire%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20plea%20for%20a%20high-level%20probe%2C%20this%20morning's%20hearing%20included%20a%20plea%20about%20the%20coaching%20centre%20running%20a%20library%20in%20the%20basement%2C%20in%20apparent%20violation%20of%20building%20codes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20Of%20Delhi%20Living%20In%20A%20Jungle...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20began%20with%20a%20strong%20statement%20from%20the%20petitioner%3B%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20living%20in%20a%20jungle%20where%20people%20are%20dying%20of%20fire%20and%20water...%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20petitioner%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20earlier%20civic%20tragedies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20also%20mention%20of%20a%20letter%20from%20June%20last%20year%20that%20the%20petition%20said%20was%20%26quot%3Bregarding%20illegal%20operation%20of%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%26quot%3B.%20No%20action%20was%20taken%2C%20it%20was%20alleged%2C%20despite%20two%20reminders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMultiple%20libraries%20are%20running%20in%20basements%20in%20residential%20areas%20(but)%20MCD%20is%20quiet.%20I%20don't%20know%20why...%20many%20sitting%20Commissioners%20have%20properties%20there.%20It%20is%20the%20bitter%20truth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petitioner%20said%2C%20arguing%20the%20civic%20body%20and%20the%20Fire%20Department%20were%20%26quot%3Bpurposely%20not%20taking%20action%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%2C%20and%20the%20petitioner's%20claim%20that%20parts%20of%20Delhi%2C%20like%20Karol%20Bagh%20and%20Rajendra%20Nagar%2C%20have%20%26quot%3Bso%20many%20(illegal)%20multi-storey%20buildings...%20in%20which%2050-60%20students%20are%20residing%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20acknowledged%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20disconnect%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20city's%20infrastructure%20and%20its%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20From%20MCD%20Gone%20To%20Jail%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20sought%20to%20know%20why%20no%20action%20had%20been%20taken%20against%20senior%20MCD%20staffers.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20your%20officers%20believe%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20comply%20with%20orders...%26quot%3B%20was%20the%20sharp%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%20only%20junior%20city%20engineers%20have%20been%20fired.%20Senior%20staff%20have%20been%20suspended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20terminated%20junior%20officers...%20but%20what%20about%20senior%20officers%20who%20should%20have%20supervised%20(their%20work)%3F%20Has%20anyone%20from%20MCD%20gone%20to%20jail%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20some%20time%20senior%20officers%20must%20visit%20(sites%2C%20but)%20they%20are%20not%20leaving%20their%20air-conditioned%20offices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BAbsolute%20Chaos%26quot%3B%2C%20Court%20Slams%20MCD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20furious%20court%20also%20questioned%20the%20competence%20of%20city%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20if%20you%20ask%20a%20MCD%20official%20to%20plan%20drains...%20they%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20it.%20They%20don't%20(even)%20know%20where%20the%20drains%20are...%20everything%20is%20mixed%20up.%20It%20is%20absolutely%20chaotic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20permitting%20multi-storey%20buildings%20but%20there%20is%20no%20proper%20drain.%20You%20have%20mixed%20sewage%20with%20storm%20water%20drain%2C%20there%20is%20reverse%20flow...%20Your%20civic%20authorities%20are%20bankrupt.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20money%20to%20pay%20salaries%2C%20then%20how%20will%20you%20upgrade%20infrastructure%3F%26quot%3B%20it%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20allowing%20six-storey%20buildings%20then%20(proper)%20infrastructure%20is%20needed.%20Your%20engineer%20must%20have%20known%20this%20situation%20is%20possible.%20Why%20did%20the%20engineer%20not%20insist%20on%20additional%20pumps%20to%20flush%20out%20excess%20water%20while%20granting%20this%20sanction%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20demanded%20of%20the%20MCD.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-government-to-introduce-new-law-to-regulate-coaching-centres-aap-6228532%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDelhi%20government%2C%C2%A0which%20intends%C2%A0to%20pass%20a%20new%20law%20to%20regulate%20coaching%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20authorities%20had%20conducted%20inspections%20and%20issued%20notices%20to%2075%20institutes.%20Thirty-five%20of%20these%20were%20shut%20and%2025%20sealed%2C%20its%20counsel%20told%20the%20court%20today%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20justifying...%20but%20action%20is%20being%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C