0day%20there%20is%20a%20flood%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20Acting%20Chief%20Justice%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20decide%20on%20this%20freebie%20culture.%20There%20is%20a%20population%20of%203.3%20crore%20people%2C%20whereas%20the%20city%20was%20planned%20for%20six%20or%20seven%20lakh.%20How%20do%20you%20plan%20to%20accommodate%20so%20many%20without%20upgrading%20infrastructure%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20infrastructural%20breakdown%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20declared%2C%20lamenting%20(predictable%20political)%20blame%20games%20that%20erupt%20after%20civic%20tragedies.%20%26quot%3BEntire%20administrative%20infrastructure%20of%20Delhi%20needs%20to%20be%20re-examine%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20also%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20discord%20between%20the%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%20Act%20and%20the%20MCD%20Act%20over%20which%20civic%20body%20is%20responsible%20for%20certain%20kinds%20of%20drains%20to%20make%20its%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722414960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fk3i9q9n8_raus-coaching-pti_625x300_29_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-civic-body-chief-summoned-by-high-court-over-coaching-centre-deaths-6229606%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20has%20slammed%20the%20city%20government%20and%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi%20Wednesday%20as%20it%20heard%20a%20plea%20for%20a%20high-level%20probe%20into%20the%20deaths%20of%20three%20students%2C%20who%20drowned%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20a%20Rajendra%20Nagar%20coaching%20centre.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22