rench%20magazine%20Madame%20Figaro%20carried%20it%20first.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fembarrassing-french-president-emmanuel-macrons-embrace-and-kiss-with-sports-minister-causes-a-stir-6229530%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fembarrassing-french-president-emmanuel-macrons-embrace-and-kiss-with-sports-minister-causes-a-stir-6229530%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fembarrassing-french-president-emmanuel-macrons-embrace-and-kiss-with-sports-minister-causes-a-stir-6229530%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BTax%20On%20Life's%20Uncertainties%26quot%3B%3A%20Nitin%20Gadkari's%20Letter%20To%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20criticism%20of%20Budget%202024%20from%20several%20quarters%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20has%20written%20to%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20requesting%20her%20to%20withdraw%20the%20GST%20imposed%20on%20premiums%20for%20life%20and%20medical%20insurance%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20has%20said%20in%20his%20letter%20that%20he%20is%20writing%20to%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20following%20a%20memorandum%20from%20the%20Nagpur%20Divisional%20Life%20Insurance%20Corporation%20Employees%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMain%20issue%20raised%20by%20the%20Union%20is%20related%20to%20withdrawal%20of%20GST%20on%20Life%20and%20Medical%20Insurance%20Premium.%20Both%20life%20insurance%20and%20medical%20insurance%20premiums%20attract%20a%20GST%20rate%20of%2018%20per%20cent.%20Levying%20GST%20on%20life%20insurance%20premium%20amounts%20to%20levying%20tax%20on%20the%20uncertainties%20of%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highways%20Minister%20has%20written.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Union%20feels%20that%20the%20person%20who%20covers%20the%20risk%20of%20life's%20uncertainties%20to%20give%20some%20protection%20to%20the%20family%20should%20not%20be%20levied%20tax%20on%20the%20premium%20to%20purchase%20cover%20against%20this%20risk.%20Similarly%2C%20the%2018%25%20GST%20on%20medical%20insurance%20premium%20is%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20deterrent%20for%20the%20growth%20of%20this%20segment%20of%20business%2C%20which%20is%20socially%20necessary.%20Therefore%2C%20they%20have%20urged%20withdrawal%20of%20GST%20as%20mentioned%20above%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari%20said%20the%20union%20that%20met%20him%20also%20raised%20points%20related%20to%20differential%20treatment%20to%20savings%20by%20way%20of%20life%20insurance%2C%20re-introduction%20of%20IT%20deduction%20for%20health%20insurance%20premium%20and%20consolidation%20of%20public%20and%20sector%20general%20insurance%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20above%2C%20you%20are%20requested%20to%20consider%20the%20suggestion%20of%20Withdrawal%20of%20GST%20on%20Life%20and%20Medical%20Insurance%20Premium%20on%20priority%20as%20it%20becomes%20cumbersome%20for%20the%20senior%20citizens%20as%20per%20rules%20with%20due%20verification%20along%20with%20other%20relevant%20points%20raised%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20BJP%20chief%20has%20said%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20Ms%20Sitharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gadkari's%20letter%20to%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20comes%20amid%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters%20over%20the%20first%20Budget%20of%20the%20third%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%2C%20presented%20last%20week.%20While%20the%20Opposition%20has%20accused%20the%20Centre%20of%20being%20generous%20only%20to%20states%20ruled%20by%20its%20key%20allies%20TDP%20and%20JDU%2C%20a%20section%20of%20social%20media%20users%20have%20pointed%20to%20high%20tax%20rates%20for%20the%20salaried%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%20has%20trashed%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%2C%20saying%20the%20Centre%20has%20provided%20funds%20to%20all%20states.%20She%20has%20said%20that%20if%20the%20name%20of%20a%20state%20is%20not%20mentioned%20in%20the%20Budget%20speech%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20it%20is%20not%20covered.%20The%20BJP%20has%20said%20policy%20priorities%20of%20the%20Budget%20suggest%20that%20it%20has%20a%20long-term%20goal%20of%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%20--%20making%20India%20a%20developed%20nation%20--%20by%202047.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722410400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fgeo371eo_nitin-gadkari-nirmala-_625x300_31_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-gst-on-life-insurance-nitin-gadkaris-appeal-to-nirmala-sitharaman-6229125%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20criticism%20of%20Budget%202024%20from%20several%20quarters%2C%20Union%20Minister%20and%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20has%20written%20to%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%2C%20requesting%20her%20to%20withdraw%20the%20GST%20imposed%20on%20premiums%20for%20life%20and%20medical%20insurance%20plans.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-gst-on-life-insurance-nitin-gadkaris-appeal-to-nirmala-sitharaman-6229125%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-gst-on-life-insurance-nitin-gadkaris-appeal-to-nirmala-sitharaman-6229125%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fremove-gst-on-life-insurance-nitin-gadkaris-appeal-to-nirmala-sitharaman-6229125%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lakshya%20starrer%20Kill%20crosses%20Rs%2023%20crore%20mark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722410252000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112159551%2Cimgsize-43326.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%