said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Temu%20acknowledged%20the%20protests%20and%20said%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bactively%20working%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20merchants%20on%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%20a%20group%20of%20merchants%20gathered%20at%20the%20office%20of%20a%20Temu%20logistics%20affiliate%20in%20Guangzhou%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20group%20%26quot%3Bincluded%20about%20a%20dozen%20sellers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20were%20unhappy%20with%20how%20Temu%20handled%20after-sales%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20quality%20and%20compliance%20of%20their%20products%2C%20disputing%20an%20amount%20worth%20several%20million%20yuan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThese%20merchants%20have%20declined%20to%20resolve%20the%20disputes%20through%20the%20normal%20arbitration%20and%20legal%20channels%20stated%20in%20the%20seller%20agreements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20China's%20social%20media%2C%20anger%20is%20mounting%20toward%20what%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20Western%20shoppers%20taking%20advantage%20of%20Chinese%20merchants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForeigners%20can%20buy%20products%20from%20Chinese%20merchants%2C%20receive%20the%20goods%2C%20and%20not%20spend%20any%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F3895107933%2FOq3t9CKT0%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030103_%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eone%20blogger%20based%20in%20Hebei.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20essentially%20moved%20the%20zero-dollar%20purchase%20practice%20from%20the%20US%20to%20here%2C%20making%20Chinese%20companies%20provide%20goods%20to%20foreigners%20for%20free.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20we%20are%20socialist%2C%20with%20strict%20supervision%20for%20enterprises%2C%20there%20are%20still%20many%20companies%20that%20do%20more%20capitalistic%20things%20than%20companies%20in%20capitalist%20countries!%26quot%3B%2