ank%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722402970000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F31%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1722402645-8707.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsanjay-shukla-assumes-charge-as-managing-director-of-national-housing-bank-124073100317_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Before%20joining%20NHB%2C%20Shukla%20was%20the%20founding%20MD%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer%20(CEO)%20of%20Centrum%20Housing%20Finance%20Limited%20(CHFL)%20from%20October%202016%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsanjay-shukla-assumes-charge-as-managing-director-of-national-housing-bank-124073100317_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsanjay-shukla-assumes-charge-as-managing-director-of-national-housing-bank-124073100317_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fsanjay-shukla-assumes-charge-as-managing-director-of-national-housing-bank-124073100317_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Secretary's%20Big%20Charge%20On%20AAP%20Minister%20After%20Basement%20Deaths%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20report%20on%20the%20basement%20tragedy%20at%20Delhi's%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20that%20left%20three%20IAS%20aspirants%20dead%2C%20Delhi%20government's%20Chief%20Secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%20has%20blamed%20the%20coaching%20centre%20for%20encroachment%20that%20blocked%20drains%20and%20accused%20minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20of%20sitting%20on%20a%20key%20legislation%20to%20tackle%20waterlogging%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20Chief%20Secretary's%20response%20after%20Mr%20Bharadwaj%2C%20who%20holds%20multiple%20portfolios%20including%20flood%20control%2C%20sought%20an%20explanation%20about%20the%20bureaucrat's%20claims%20of%20pending%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Secretary%20has%20said%20that%20a%20meeting%20was%20convened%20after%20heavy%20rain%20last%20year%20led%20to%20waterlogging%20in%20the%20city%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20comprehensive%20strategy%20to%20prevent%20flooding%2C%20according%20to%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20found%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20consolidate%20drainage%20management%20in%20Delhi%20for%2018%20years%20and%20emphasised%20on%20the%20requirement%20for%20a%20Storm%20Water%20and%20Drainage%20Act%20with%20penal%20provisions%20for%20encroachment%20and%20dumping%20of%20waste%20into%20these%20drains.%20The%20meeting%20also%20called%20for%20a%20Master%20Drainage%20Plan%20for%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20findings%2C%20he%20has%20said%2C%20were%20submitted%20to%20the%20minister%20in%20August%202023%20and%20remained%20with%20him%20for%20consideration%20till%20February%20this%20year.%20It%20was%20only%20after%20that%20gap%20of%20five%20months%20that%20the%20minister%20asked%20for%20a%20presentation%2C%20the%20senior%20official%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20added%20that%20the%20Irrigation%20and%20Flood%20Control%20Department%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20decision%20yet%20on%20bringing%20a%20Storm%20Water%20and%20Drainage%20Act.%20On%20the%20Master%20Drainage%20Plan%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20has%20said%20that%20an%20IIT%20Delhi%20report%20on%20this%20was%20not%20accepted%20by%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20government.%20It%20was%20then%20decided%20that%20three%20separate%20drainage%20plans%20would%20be%20prepared%2C%20but%20no%20substantive%20work%20has%20taken%20place%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20Storm%20Water%20Drainage%20Act%20is%20still%20pending%20with%20the%20minister%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20such%20a%20legislation%20would%20impact%20the%20rainwater%20management%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20storm%20water%20drainage%20system%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20has%20said%2C%20cannot%20be%20controlled%20without%20a%20proper%20legislative%20framework%20and%20this%20situation%20leads%20to%20flooding%20in%20several%20areas%20whenever%20there%20is%20heavy%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20Basement%20Tragedy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20incident%2C%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20has%20pointed%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20probe%20conducted%20by%20the%20Municipal%20Corporation%20of%20Delhi.%20The%20construction%20of%20ramps%20in%20violation%20of%20norms%20has%20blocked%20the%20entry%20of%20drains%20through%20which%20rainwater%20can%20be%20drained%20out%2C%20the%20report%20says.%20Manholes%20and%20drains%20in%20the%20area%20have%20been%20covered%20by%20granite%20or%20marble%20or%20kota%20stones%2C%20and%20this%20has%20made%20cleaning%20of%20drains%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20every%20time%20there%20is%20heavy%20rain%2C%20water%20accumulates%20on%20the%20road%20along%20which%20the%20coaching%20centres%20are%20located.%20This%20water%2C%20which%20should%20have%20been%20disposed%20off%20through%20drains%2C%20moves%20towards%20the%20parking%20area%20and%20the%20basements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%2C%20where%20Saturday's%20tragedy%20took%20place%2C%20the%20drainage%20system%20has%20been%20blocked%20completely%20and%20no%20safeguards%20to%20meet%20any%20eventuality%20are%20in%20the%20place%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Blame%20Game%20Continues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Chief%20Secretary's%20report%20is%20the%20latest%20episode%20in%20the%20blame%20game%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20basement%20tragedy.%20The%20deaths%20of%20Tanya%20Soni%2C%20Shreya%20Yadav%20and%20Nevin%20Dalwin%20have%20sparked%20massive%20protests%20by%20students%20who%20blame%20civic%20negligence%20for%20the%20tragedy.%20The%20Opposition%20BJP%20has%20targeted%20the%20ruling%20AAP%2C%20which%20also%20controls%20the%20MCD.%20AAP%20has%20hit%20back%2C%20alleging%20a%20big%20conspiracy%20and%20corruption%20in%20desilting%20work%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%20Minister%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20that%20the%20work%20of%20removing%20silt%20from%20drains%20and%20sewers%20was%20not%20done%20properly%20due%20to%20the%20negligence%20of%20officers%20of%20PWD%2C%20MCD%20and%20Irrigation%20and%20Flood%20Control%20Department.%20He%20said%20that%20Delhi%20government%20can%20neither%20transfer%20these%20officers%20nor%20take%20any%20action%20against%20them%20and%20only%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%20can%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP's%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20MLA%20Durgesh%20Pathak%20has%20questioned%20why%20no%20work%20on%20Delhi's%20drainage%20system%20was%20done%20in%20the%20past%2015-20%20years.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20should%20have%20shame.%20We%20demand%20action%20against%20all%20officers%2C%20including%20the%20senior%20officers%20who%20are%20found%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722402900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv219irn8_saurabh-bharadwaj_625x300_21_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-basement-tragedy-saurabh-bharadwaj-delhi-chief-secretarys-big-charge-on-aap-minister-after-basement-deaths-6228664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20his%20report%20on%20the%20basement%20tragedy%20at%20Delhi's%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20that%20left%20three%20IAS%20aspirants%20dead%2C%20Delhi%20government's%20Chief%20Secretary%20Naresh%20Kumar%20has%20blamed%20the%20coaching%20centre%20for%20encroachment%20that%20blocked%20drains%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-basement-tragedy-saurabh-bharadwaj-delhi-chief-se