%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hamas%20leader%20Ismail%20Haniyeh%20was%20assassinated%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20morning%20in%20Iran%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20describing%20the%20strike%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsevere%20escalation%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20not%20achieve%20its%20goals.%20Iran's%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20confirmed%20the%20death%20of%20Haniyeh%2C%20hours%20after%20he%20attended%20a%20swearing%20in%20ceremony%20for%20the%20country's%20new%20president%2C%20and%20said%20it%20was%20investigating.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhamas-leader-ismail-haniyeh-killed-in-tehran-whats-next-for-irans-axis-of-resistance%2Farticleshow%2F112152448.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Auction%3A%20Top%20Franchise%20Wants%208%20Retentions%2C%20BCCI%20Likely%20To%20Agree%20On...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20could%20be%20a%20consensus%20about%20increasing%20the%20team%20purse%20up%20to%20Rs%20120%20crore%20and%20retentions%20up%20to%20six%2C%20including%20'Right%20To%20Match'%20(RTM)%20options%2C%20during%20the%20IPL's%20Governing%20Council's%20meeting%20with%20the%20owners%20of%20all%2010%20franchises%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Wednesday.%20With%20a%20big%20auction%20scheduled%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20year%2C%20the%20modalities%20need%20to%20be%20set%20in%20order%20and%20five%20points%20will%20be%20on%20the%20agenda%20of%20the%20BCCI-team%20owners%20meeting%20where%20divergent%20views%20could%20emerge%20on%20some%20of%20the%20points.%20While%20BCCI%20won't%20announce%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20on%20team%20building%2C%20the%20inputs%20from%20the%20owners%20will%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20spoke%20to%20multiple%20franchises%20and%20there%20was%20one%20aspect%20where%20everyone%20agreed%20that%20the%20current%20team%20purse%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20needs%20to%20be%20increased%20by%20at%20least%2020%20to%2025%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20(increase%20of%20purse)%20is%20happening%20for%20sure.%20The%20standard%20increase%20should%20be%20anywhere%20between%2020%20to%2025%20percent%20and%20hence%20anything%20in%20the%20range%20of%20Rs%20120%20crore%20to%20125%20crore%20will%20be%20a%20fair%20deal.%20Most%20franchises%20would%20agree%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20of%20one%20of%20the%20IPL%20franchises%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bigger%20issue%20is%20the%20player%20retention%20where%20it%20could%20be%20difficult%20to%20reach%20a%20common%20ground%20as%20most%20teams%20have%20different%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20one%20powerful%20franchise%20seemed%20to%20have%20suggested%20as%20many%20as%20eight%20retentions%2C%20including%20RTMs%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20others%20will%20agree%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20IPL%20allows%20four%20retention%20per%20year%20with%20three%20being%20Indians%20and%20one%20overseas.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20most%20teams%20want%20retention%20to%20be%20between%20five%20to%20six.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20continuity%20and%20maintaining%20a%20core%20is%20very%20important%20going%20forward.%20May%20be%20allow%20six%20(retentions)%20including%20a%20couple%20of%20RTM%20cards%20with%20at%20least%20one%20uncapped%20player%20being%20kept%20in%20the%20mix.%20But%20there%20could%20be%20some%20debate%20over%20the%20number%20of%20overseas%20retentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20teams%20like%20Delhi%20Capitals%20(Jake%20Fraser-McGurk%20and%20Tristan%20Stubbs)%20and%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(Pat%20Cummins%2C%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%20and%20Travis%20Head)%2C%20who%20would%20want%20more%20than%20one%20overseas%20retention%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20IPL%20source%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20bone%20of%20contention%20could%20be%20the%20'Impact%20Player'%20rule%20and%20while%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20winning%20skipper%20Rohit%20Sharma%20and%20star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20have%20both%20spoken%20openly%20about%20how%20it%20can%20affect%20the%20development%20of%20all-rounders%2C%20none%20of%20the%20franchises%20would%20mind%20a%20contest%20where%2012%20players%20will%20be%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20in%20the%20business%20of%20cricket%20and%20it%20is%20possibly%20BCCI's%20duty%20to%20protect%20all-rounders%2C%20who%20are%20becoming%20rare%20because%20of%20this%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20the%20counter%20argument%20by%20a%20franchise%20like%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20could%20be%20that%20the%20'Impact%20Player'%20rule%20would%20allow%20their%20talisman%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20to%20continue%20for%20one%20more%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Impact%20Player%20rule%20is%20gone%2C%20Dhoni%2C%20who%20nowadays%20comes%20in%20at%20No.%208%20can't%20afford%20to%20do%20that%20and%20also%20have%20Shivam%20Dube%20in%20the%20playing%20XI%20without%20utilising%20his%20bowling%20which%20is%20cannon%20fodder%20for%20the%20batters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20also%20be%20discussions%20on%20IPL%20Gaming%20Rights%20and%20revenue%20sharing%20from%20IPL's%20Central%20Merchandising%20pool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722401940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fr1va0jfg_ms-dhoni-and-ruturaj-gaikwad-x_625x300_31_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fipl-2025-auction-top-franchise-wants-8-retentions-says-report-bcci-likely-to-agree-on-5-6-6225250%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20one%20powerful%20franchise%20seemed%20to%20have%20suggested%20as%20m