%20at%20the%20coaching%20centre%20in%20Delhi%20but%2021-year-old%20Rishabh%20Pal%20says%20he%20will%20forever%20feel%20guilty%20for%20not%20being%20able%20to%20save%20his%20fellow%20students%20including%20Tanya%20Soni%20who%20had%20spurred%20him%20not%20to%20give%20up%20hope%20when%20he%20feared%20that%20their%20end%20was%20near.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Ghaziabad%2C%20was%20among%20the%2025-30%20students%20who%20were%20trapped%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20building%20on%20the%20July%2027%20evening%2C%20where%20Tanya%2C%20Shreya%20Yadav%20and%20Nevin%20Dalvin%20died%20due%20to%20flooding%20following%20rain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20in%20the%20library%20when%20the%20water%20started%20entering%20the%20building.%20About%2010%20to%2012%20students%2C%20who%20were%20near%20the%20gate%2C%20managed%20to%20rush%20out%20but%20about%2010-15%20of%20us%20got%20trapped%20due%20to%20the%20heavy%20flow%20of%20the%20water%20on%20the%20stairs%2C%26quot%3B%20Rishabh%2C%20a%20civil%20services%20aspirant%20from%20batch%20M33%20at%20Rau's%20IAS%20Study%20Circle%20that%20started%20in%20June%2C%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20said%20they%20had%20lost%20hope%20and%20thought%20all%20of%20them%20would%20die.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20Tanya%2C%20who%20was%20my%20batchmate%2C%20said%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20panic%20and%20we%20would%20be%20saved.%20She%20also%20said%3A%20'Let's%20form%20a%20human%20chain'.%20We%20tried%20forming%20the%20chain%20but%20due%20to%20the%20flow%20of%20water%20we%20could%20not%20hold%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20water%20kept%20gushing%20in%2C%20Tanya%20and%20Shreya%20stood%20on%20a%20table.%20I%20somehow%20mustered%20courage%20and%20started%20climbing%20the%20stairs.%20Halfway%20along%20the%20stairs%2C%20a%20housekeeping%20staff%20extended%20his%20hand%20towards%20me%20and%20pulled%20me%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Rishabh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBehind%20me%2C%20my%20friend%20Jaideep%20and%20a%20few%20others%20came%20out.%20Then%2C%20the%20staff%20members%20of%20our%20institute%20brought%20a%20rope%20to%20pull%20the%20others%20who%20were%20stuck%20in%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20said%20Tanya%20and%20Shreya%20might%20not%20have%20moved%20towards%20the%20stairs%20as%20they%20may%20have%20been%20scared%20of%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20water%20gushing%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20about%20Nevin%20as%20I%20did%20not%20notice%20him%20in%20the%20library.%20He%20might%20have%20been%20in%20the%20toilet%20at%20that%20point%20in%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20had%20very%20little%20time%20to%20react%20as%20within%205-10%20seconds%2C%20they%20were%20in%20knee-deep%20water%20and%20things%20took%20a%20turn%20for%20the%20worse%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNakul%20came%20out%20last%20and%20informed%20us%20that%20two%20more%20girls%20(Tanya%20and%20Shreya)%20were%20still%20there.%20In%20just%20three%20to%20four%20minutes%2C%20the%20over%2013-ft-high%20library%20was%20filled%20with%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20lives%20with%20his%20parents%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ghaziabad.%20He%20has%20paid%20Rs%201.75%20lakh%20for%20his%20one-year%20course%20at%20the%20institute.%20His%20father%20is%20employed%20in%20a%20private%20company%20while%20his%20elder%20brother%20works%20in%20an%20IT%20company%20in%20Noida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20all%20the%20staff%20members%20helped%20in%20rescuing%20the%20trapped%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20staff%20member%2C%20including%20the%20uncle%20in%20the%20library%2C%20helped%20us%20in%20saving%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20students.%20Had%20they%20not%20acted%20swiftly%2C%20the%20number%20of%20causalities%20would%20have%20been%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20said%20there%20was%20no%20biometric%20lock%20system%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20clarify%20that%20there%20was%20no%20biometric%20system%20in%20the%20basement%20or%20any%20part%20of%20the%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20there%20were%20two%20entry%20and%20exit%20points%20from%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20a%20delay%20in%20response%20by%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20NDRF%20officials%20who%20came%20at%20about%2010%20pm%20told%20us%20that%20they%20could%20not%20do%20anything%20as%20they%20did%20not%20have%20any%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20institute%20was%20illegally%20constructed%20but%20all%20the%20faculty%20members%20who%20were%20present%20in%20the%20building%20helped%20us%20in%20the%20rescue%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20was%20struggling%20to%20come%20out%2C%20Rishabh%20was%20injured%20by%20the%20shards%20of%20broken%20glass%20in%20the%20library.%20He%20was%20given%20first%20aid%20and%20taken%20to%20Ganga%20Ram%20Hospital%20for%20further%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERishabh%20said%20that%20he%20wishes%20for%20early%20justice%20for%20the%20victims%20and%20punishment%20for%20those%20responsible%20for%20the%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20and%20other%20fellow%20students%20of%20the%20institute%20should%20not%20be%20affected%20as%20they%20have%20paid%20hefty%20fees%20for%20coaching.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722399840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fhtg61su_delhi-coaching-institute-basement_625x300_28_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-