ift-themed%20party%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tmz.com%2F2024%2F07%2F30%2Fteachers-hero-critical-condition-saving-kids-taylor-swift-mass-stabbing%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ETMZ%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20Leanne%20Lucas%20acted%20quickly%20to%20get%20children%20to%20safety%20through%20a%20fire%20escape%2C%20while%20her%20colleague%2C%20Heidi%20Barlow%2C%20locked%20others%20in%20a%20bathroom%20stall%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20a%20knife-wielding%20attacker%20who%20rampaged%20through%20the%20yoga%20and%20dance%20event%20in%20Southport%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20women%20are%20now%20in%20critical%20condition.%20Leanne's%20aunt%2C%20Pauline%20Bennett%2C%20shared%20that%20Leanne%20is%20awaiting%20surgery%20and%20that%20her%20only%20concern%20was%20protecting%20the%20children.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20her%20small%20frame%2C%20she%20couldn't%20stand%20a%20chance%20against%20the%20attacker.%20Leanne's%20family%20is%20hoping%20and%20praying%20for%20her%20recovery%2C%20while%20Heidi's%20exact%20condition%20remains%20unclear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerseyside%20Police%20Chief%20Constable%20Serena%20Kennedy%20confirmed%20that%20two%20children%20died%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20with%20a%20third%20confirmed%20dead%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%20The%20motive%20for%20the%20attack%20is%20still%20unknown.%20The%20suspect%2C%20a%2017-year-old%2C%20was%20seen%20pacing%20outside%20a%20home%2020%20minutes%20before%20the%20incident%20and%20was%20later%20apprehended%20and%20questioned%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20has%20been%20so%20shocking%20that%20even%20Taylor%20Swift%20herself%20said%20she%20was%20completely%20stunned%20by%20the%20attack%2C%20and%20members%20of%20the%20Royal%20family%20have%20spoken%20out%20about%20the%20terror.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMerseyside%20police%20said%20that%20three%20young%20girls%2C%20ages%206%2C7%20and%209%2C%20were%20stabbed%20to%20death%20in%20the%20horrifying%20midday%20attack%20on%20Monday%2C%20while%20eight%20other%20children%20were%20stabbed%2C%20including%20five%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20the%20adults%20who%20were%20injured%20were%20bravely%20trying%20to%20protect%20the%20children%20who%20were%20being%20attacked%2C%26quot%3B%20Merseyside%20Police%20Chief%20Constable%20Serena%20Kennedy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20the%20Monday%20attack%2C%20prayers%20for%20Lucas%2C%20who%20owns%20Enlighten-%20the%20company%20that%20organised%20the%20event%2C%20quickly%20began%20popping%20up%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20absolutely%20devastated.%20Please%20please%20pray%20for%20Leanne%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunshine%20Yoga%2C%20another%20local%20studio%2C%20wrote%20on%20Facebook%20in%20a%20since-deleted%20post%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeanne%20came%20on%20my%20training%20course%20in%20December.%20A%20beautiful%20young%20creative%20girl%20who%20was%20so%20passionate%20about%20helping%20children.%20I%20just%20can't%20believe%20it.%20Please%20pray%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20studio%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722399180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fd90d35d8_leanne-lucas-and-heidi-barlow_625x300_31_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhero-teachers-critical-after-saving-children-from-mass-stabbing-at-taylor-swift-themed-event-6228293%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Merseyside%20Police%20Chief%20Constable%20Serena%20Kennedy%20confirmed%20that%20two%20children%20died%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20with%20a%20third%20confirmed%20dead%20on%20Tuesday%20morning.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fhero-teachers-critical-after-saving-children-from-mass-stabbing-at-taylor-swift-themed-event-6228293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Studies%20Point%20To%20What%20Lead%20To%20Devastating%20Wayanad%20Landslides%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EClimate%20change%2C%20fragile%20terrain%20and%20loss%20of%20forest%20cover%20created%20the%20perfect%20recipe%20for%20the%20devastating%20landslides%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20district%20that%20claimed%20123%20lives%2C%20according%20to%20studies%20conducted%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtremely%20heavy%20rain%20triggered%20a%20series%20of%20landslides%20in%20the%20hilly%20areas%20of%20Wayanad%20early%20Tuesday.%20While%20128%20people%20were%20injured%2C%20many%20are%20feared%20trapped%20under%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20landslide%20atlas%20released%20by%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation's%20(ISRO)%20National%20Remote%20Sensing%20Centre%20last%20year%2C%2010%20out%20of%20the%2030%20most%20landslide-prone%20districts%20in%20India%20were%20in%20Kerala%2C%20with%20Wayanad%20ranked%2013th.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%200.09%20million%20square%20kilometres%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20and%20the%20Konkan%20hills%20(Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Goa%20and%20Maharashtra)%20were%20prone%20to%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20vulnerability%20of%20inhabitants%20and%20households%20is%20more%20significant%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20due%20to%20the%20very%20high%20population%20and%20household%20density%2C%20especially%20in%20Kerala%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20study%20published%20by%20Springer%20in%202021%20said%20all%20landslide%20hotspots%20in%20Kerala%20were%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20region%20and%20concentrated%20in%20Idukki%2C%20Ernakulam%2C%20Kottayam%2C%20Wayanad%2C%20Kozhikode%20and%20Malappuram%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20about%2059%20per%20cent%20of%20total%20landslides%20in%20Kerala%20occurred%20in%20plantation%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202022%20study%20on%20depleting%20forest%20cover%20in%20Wayanad%20showed%20that%2062%20per%20cent%20of%20forests%20in%20the%20district%20disappeared%20between%201950%20and%202018%20while%20plantation%20cover%20rose%20by%20around%201%2C800%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%2C%20published%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Environmental%20Research%20and%20Public%20Health%2C%20said%20around%2085%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20area%20of%20Wayanad%20was%20under%20forest%20cover%20until%20the%201950s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20scientists%2C%20climate%20change%20was%20increasing%20the%20possibility%20of%20landslides%20in%20the%20Western%20Ghats%2C%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20%26quot%3Bhottest%20hotspots%26quot%3B%20of%20biological%20diversity%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ES%20Abhilash%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Advanced%20Centre%20for%20Atmospheric%20Radar%20Research%20at%20Cochin%20University%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20(CUSAT)%2C%20told%20PTI%20that%20warming%20of%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20was%20allowing%20the%20formation%20of%20deep%20cloud%20systems%2C%20leading%20to%20extremely%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20Kerala%20in%20a%20short%20period%20and%20increasing%20the%20possibility%20of%20landslides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20research%20found%20that%20the%20southeast%20Arabian%20Sea%20is%20becoming%20warmer%2C%20causing%20the%20atmosphere%20above%20this%20region%2C%20including%20Kerala%2C%20to%20become%20thermodynamically%20unstable%2C%26quot%3B%20Abhilash%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20atmospheric%20instability%2C%20allowing%20the%20formation%20of%20deep%20clouds%2C%20is%20linked%20to%20climate%20change.%20Earlier%2C%20this%20kind%20of%20rainfall%20was%20more%20common%20in%20the%20northern%20Konkan%20belt%2C%20north%20of%20Mangalore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResearch%20by%20Abhilash%20and%20other%20scientists%20published%20in%20the%20npj%20Climate%20and%20Atmospheric%20Science%20journal%20in%202022%20found%20that%20rainfall%20over%20the%20west%20coast%20of%20India%20was%20becoming%20more%20convective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConvective%20rainfall%20is%20often%20characterised%20by%20intense%2C%20short-duration%20showers%20or%20thunderstorms%20in%20a%20small%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20study%20by%20Abhilash%20and%20scientists%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Tropical%20Meteorology%20and%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%2C%20published%20in%20Elsevier%20in%202021%2C%20found%20that%20one%20of%20the%20hotspots%20of%20heavy%20rainfall%20in%20the%20Konkan%20region%20(between%2014%20degrees%20north%20and%2016%20degrees%20north)%20seemed%20to%20have%20shifted%20southward%2C%20with%20likely%20fatal%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20increase%20in%20rainfall%20intensity%20may%20suggest%20a%20rising%20probability%20of%20landslides%20in%20the%20high%20to%20mid-land%20slopes%20of%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20in%20eastern%20Kerala%20during%20the%20monsoon%20seasons%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20landslides%20also%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20the%20unheeded%20warnings%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BWestern%20Ghats%20Ecology%20Expert%20Panel%26quot%3B%20set%20up%20by%20the%20government%20under%20ecologist%20Madhav%20Gadgil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Centre%20in%202011%2C%20recommending%20that%20the%20entire%20hill%20range%20be%20declared%20an%20ecologically%20sensitive%20area%20and%20divided%20into%20ecologically%20sensitive%20zones%20based%20on%20their%20ecological%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20recommended%20a%20ban%20on%20mining%2C%20quarrying%2C%20new%20thermal%20power%20plants%2C%20hydropower%20projects%20and%20large-scale%20wind%20energy%20projects%20in%20ecologically%20sensitive%20zone%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recommendations%20have%20not%20been%20implemented%20even%20after%2014%20years%20due%20to%20resistance%20from%20state%20governments%2C%20industries%20and%20local%20communities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%