t%20these%20youth%20at%20signals%20in%20metropolitan%20cities%2C%20where%20they%20otherwise%20engage%20in%20seasonal%20begging.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20around%2040%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20district%20living%20in%20hamlets.%20They%20do%20not%20even%20possess%20an%20Aadhaar%20Card%20or%20birth%20certificate%2C%20nor%20go%20to%20school%20or%20work.%20Their%20main%20income%20comes%20from%20robbing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20it%20easy%20to%20convince%20these%20people%20to%20change%20their%20mindsets%3F%20%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20but%20I%20go%20personally%20knocking%20on%20their%20doors%2C%E2%80%9D%20responds%20Kulkarni.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20quest%20to%20better%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%20only%20grows%20with%20every%20passing%20day.%20And%20so%2C%20Parth%E2%80%99s%20newfound%20freedom%20is%20of%20special%20significance%20to%20Kulkarni%2C%20who%20is%20thrilled%20he%20was%20able%20to%20contribute%20to%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20goes%20beyond%20duty.%20It%E2%80%99s%20an%20inner%20calling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-66038795%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOsmanabad%3A%20The%20tortured%20Indian%20labourers%20who%20were%20kept%20as%20slaves%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Pravin%20Thakre%20in%20Osmanabad%20and%20Zoya%20Mateen%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Published%20on%2029%20June%2C%202023.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flabour.gov.in%2Fbonded-labour%23%3A~%3Atext%3D1975%2520with%2520the%2520enactment%2520of%2Ccognizable%2520offence%2520punishable%2520by%2520law.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C