2%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Folympics-2024-tom-daley-reflects-on-his-journey-after-taking-diving-silver-13187163%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Folympics-2024-tom-daley-reflects-on-his-journey-after-taking-diving-silver-13187163%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Folympics-2024-tom-daley-reflects-on-his-journey-after-taking-diving-silver-13187163%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CA%20Final%202024%3A%20Siblings%20With%20AIR%201%20and%2018%20Share%20Preparation%20Tips%2C%20Planning%20Secrets%20%26amp%3B%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20can%20be%20divided%20into%20two%20sets%20of%20people%3A%20those%20who%20like%20to%20study%20alone%20and%20those%20who%20prefer%20a%20study%20buddy.%20I%20fall%20into%20the%20latter%20category%2C%20as%20having%20someone%20in%20the%20same%20boat%20as%20you%20to%20motivate%20you%20and%20answer%20your%20queries%20is%20a%20boon.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20fun%2C%20as%20you%20have%20someone%20to%20discuss%20doubts%20with%20during%20break%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20if%20this%20study%20buddy%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20house%E2%80%94your%20sibling%3F%20This%20is%20usually%20a%20rarity%20unless%20the%20sibling%20is%20a%20twin%2C%20but%20these%20siblings%20from%20Morena%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349546%2Fakshata-krishnamurthy-nasa-aerospace-engineer-rocket-scientist-space-career-mit%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheights%20that%20can%20be%20achieved%20together.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20(24)%20and%20Nandini%20(22)%20Agrawal%2C%20although%20two%20years%20apart%2C%20were%20in%20the%20same%20class%20since%20Class%202.%20Nandini%20skipped%20two%20classes%20and%20joined%20her%20brother%20in%20his%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20paths%20intertwined%20as%20they%20decided%20on%20a%20singular%20goal%3A%20to%20add%20two%20letters%20before%20their%20name%20%E2%80%94%20CA%20(Chartered%20Accountant).%20The%20duo%20worked%20together%20towards%20achieving%20this%20goal%2C%20choosing%20the%20same%20coaching%20class%20and%20the%20same%20city%20for%20their%20articleships.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20efforts%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20how!%20Both%20of%20them%20achieved%20ranks%20in%20the%20CA%20Final%20in%202021.%20The%20icing%20on%20the%20cake%20was%20that%20Nandini%20set%20a%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20by%20becoming%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20youngest%20female%20chartered%20accountant%20with%20AIR%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20how%20they%20achieved%20this%20tremendous%20feat%2C%20along%20with%20tips%20for%20aspiring%20CAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20singular%20focus%20since%20Class%207%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESachin%20recalls%20that%20his%20sister%20was%20%E2%80%9Cextraordinary%20from%20the%20beginning%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20mother%20would%20teach%20her%20at%20home%2C%20covering%20whatever%20Sachin%20was%20being%20taught%20at%20school.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20she%20already%20knew%20what%20was%20being%20taught%20in%20Class%201%2C%20my%20mother%20asked%20the%20school%20to%20enrol%20her%20in%20the%20next%20class%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sachin%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358958%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20Class%2012%2C%20the%20siblings%20studied%20in%20their%20hometown%20and%20by%20themselves%2C%20with%20no%20extra%20coaching.%20They%20topped%20their%20district%20in%20Class%2012.%20Crystal%20clear%20about%20pursuing%20CA%2C%20they%20cleared%20the%20CPT%20(Common%20Proficiency%20Test)%2C%20the%20first%20level%20of%20the%20course%2C%20after%20Class%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20CA%20Intermediate%20(the%20next%20exam)%2C%20we%20first%20went%20to%20Delhi%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F335548%2Fthis-hero-turned-mud-walls-into-blackboards-streets-into-schools-for-10000-children%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elook%20for%20coaching%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20after%20doing%20self-study%20for%20so%20long%2C%20sitting%20in%20a%20class%20of%201%2C000%20students%20seemed%20impossible.%20We%20decided%20to%20opt%20for%20online%20coaching%2C%20which%20would%20help%20us%20study%20at%20our%20pace%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sachin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20in%202017%2C%20much%20before%20online%20lectures%20were%20the%20norm.%20Using%20online%20lectures%2C%20the%20duo%20prepared%20for%20the%20inter%20exams%20from%20Morena%2C%20and%20cleared%20the%20exam%20on%20the%20first%20attempt%20in%20May%202018.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20eight%20subjects%20split%20into%20two%20groups%20in%20Inter%2C%20and%20while%20some%20people%20advised%20us%20to%20take%20one%20group%