ir%20study%20leave%20started.%20The%20first%20subject%20they%20picked%20up%20in%20December%20was%20taxation.%20Their%20plan%20was%20divided%20into%2015-day%20chunks%2C%20each%20covering%20one%20practical%20and%20one%20theory%20subject.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nandini%20and%20Sachin%20coached%20and%20motivated%20each%20other%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-43-1722258275-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358959%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENandini%20and%20Sachin%20coached%20and%20motivated%20each%20other%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20exam%20had%20eight%20subjects%20at%20that%20time%2C%20they%20completed%20their%20first%20revision%20in%20two%20months.%20They%20referred%20to%20The%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20modules%20and%20past%20papers%2C%20and%20took%20some%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20revision%20included%20trying%20to%20solve%20past%20papers%2C%20which%20gave%20them%20an%20idea%20about%20which%20areas%20needed%20more%20focus.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20targeted%2010%20d