%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fca-final-1722243562-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358909%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStudy%20buddies%20Nandini%20and%20Sachin%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20working%20on%20the%20feedback%2C%20they%20were%20better%20prepared.%20While%20the%20exams%20are%20usually%20held%20in%20May%20each%20year%2C%20in%202021%2C%20owing%20to%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20were%20postponed%20to%20July.%20Those%20two%20extra%20months%20served%20as%20a%20major%20boon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20didn%E2%80%99t%20let%20their%20guard%20down%20even%20with%20the%20extra%20time%E2%80%94they%20had%20their%20eyes%20on%20the%20prize.%20They%20did%20another%20revision%20and%20solved%20past%20papers%2C%20revision%20test%20papers%2C%20and%20mock%20test%20papers.%20For%20subjects%20they%20found%20difficult%2C%20like%20SFM%2C%20they%20spent%20extra%20time%2C%20which%20proved%20useful%20as%20they%20scored%20very%20well%20in%20it!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F348078%2Fdelhi-constable-than-singh-ki-pathshala-teaches-underprivileged-children-for-free%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocused%20and%20studied%20hard%20%3C%2Fa%3Eright%20from%20the%20start%20to%20ensure%20that%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20stress%20too%20much%20before%20the%20exam.%20Spend%20more%20time%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20your%20study%20holidays.%20This%20will%20increase%20your%20confidence%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nandini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreparation%20tips%20from%20the%20CA%20rankers%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStart%20full-blown%20preparation%20six%20to%20seven%20months%20before%20the%20exam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFinish%20your%20lectures%20as%20soon%20as%20possible%20to%20focus%20on%20self-study.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStudy%20from%20the%20ICAI%20modules%2C%20past%20question%20papers%2C%20and%20revision%20test%20papers.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMake%20a%20proper%20plan%20and%20stick%20to%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBe%20consistent%20and%20focused.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Nandini%20Agrawal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722260168000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FInfographic-website-27-1722258270.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358900%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sachin%20and%20Nandini%20Agrawal%20had%20a%20single%20goal%20since%20childhood%20--%20to%20become%20chartered%20accountants.%20Two%20years%20apart%20in%20age%2C%20the%20siblings%20cleared%20CA%20exams%20together%2C%20with%20Nandini%20becoming%20the%20youngest%20CA%20in%20the%20world.%20Here's%20how%20they%20prepared.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358900%2Fchartered-accountant-siblings-cracked-ca-together-final-exam-tips-lessons-study-plan-articleship-madhya-pradesh%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Natural%20Farming%2C%20Solar%20Energy%20%26amp%3B%20More%3A%20Will%20Budget%202024%20Push%20India%20to%20a%20Greener%20Future%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20focus%20was%20on%20employment%2C%20skills%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20(MSMEs)%20and%20farmers%2C%20there%20were%20some%20interesting%20new%20ideas%20presented%20in%20the%20latest%20Budget%20by%20Finance%20Secretary%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20on%2023%20July%20to%20make%20India%20greener.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20agriculture%2C%20the%20government%20strengthened%20its%20support%20for%20natural%20farming.%20Originally%20spear-headed%20by%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%2C%20natural%20farming%20(then%20known%20as%20zero-budget%20natural%20farming)%20was%20first%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20Budget%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20reiterated%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20initiate%20one%20crore%20farmers%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F220301%2Fpunjab-farmer-organic-vegetables-family-health-wife-safe-natural-food-india-ang136%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%20techniques%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20plans%20to%20open%2010%2C000%20bio-input%20resource%20centres%2C%20and%20has%20promised%20resources%20to%20help%20customers%20locate%20and%20differentiate%20natural%20produce%20from%20chemical-based%20agriculture%20by%20providing%20improved%20branding%20and%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrop%20breeding%20research%20will%20be%20focussed%20on%20again%20in%20response%20to%20the%20threat%20of%20climate%20change.%20The%20government%20plans%20to%20release%20109%20climate-adapted%2C%20high-yielding%20varieties%20of%2032%20horticulture%20and%20cereal%20crops.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESalient%20features%20of%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F256076%2Fhow-to-single-use-plastic-ban-rules-states-india-waste-management-reduce-reuse-sustainable-civis%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechniques%20used%20in%20natural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20based%20on%20the%20scientific%20and%20ecological%20insights%20of%20our%20ancestors%2C%20stress%20on%20the%20creation%20of%20healthy%20carbon-rich%20soil%20ecosystems%20using%20bio-inputs%20to%20stimulate%20fungi%20and%20microbes%2C%20along%20with%20cropping%20systems%20integrating%20trees%2C%20crops%2C%20herbs%20and%20livestock.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20great%20diversity%20of%20crops%20within%20a%20field%20provides%20the%20farmer%20resilience%20against%20the%20failure%20of%20one%20crop%20as%20well%20as%20providing%20habitat%20for%20natural%20predators%20that%20control%20pests.%20The%20tenets%20of%20natural%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20applying%20cow%20manure%20and%20urine%20to%20the%20seeds%20and%20soil%2C%20maintaining%20year-round%20soil-cover%2C%20banning%20crop%20burning%2C%20replacing%20monocultures%20with%20a%20mosaic%20of%20trees%2C%20shrubs%2C%20and%20herbs%C2%A0%20%E2%80%94%20is%20now%20common%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farms%20which%20have%20adopted%20this%20technique%20have%20slashed%20input%20costs%20along%20with%20the%20use%20of%20irrigation%20water%2C%20while%20maintaining%20incomes%20and%20producing%20healthier%20food%20that%20commands%20premium%20prices%20in%20the%20markets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20transport%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20major%20themes%20of%20the%20Budget%20was%20to%20plough%20improved%20public%20finances%20into%20increased%20infrastructure%20spending.%20Apart%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350255%2Fchhavi-rajawat-sarpanch-mba-soda-village-rajasthan-water-roads-college-digital-literacy-help-farmers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espending%20on%20roads%20and%20railways%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20was%20an%20intriguing%20announcement%20to%20fund%20the%20development%20of%20Transport%20Oriented%20Development%20(TOD)%20plans%20for%2014%20large%20cities%20with%20more%20than%203%20million%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20still%20at%20an%20early%20stage%2C%20if%20the%20TOD%20plan%20succeeds%2C%20it%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20transform%20urban%20living.%20Though%20still%20novel%20in%20India%2C%20TOD%20is%20common%20in%20many%20east%20Asian%20countries.%20Such%20developments%20create%20highly%20liveable%2C%20compact%20neighbourhoods%20where%20public%20transport%20and%20walking%20are%20favoured%20over%20motor%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20basic%20concept%20is%20for%20planners%20to%20grant%20new%20developments%20around%20metro%20stations%20with%20high%20Floor-to-Area-Ratios%2C%20restrict%20residential%20parking%20spaces%20and%20improve%20pedestrian%20facilities%20using%20tunnels%2C%20bridges%20and%20covered%20footpaths.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong%20has%20used%20TOD%20since%20the%201970s.%20The%20development%20board%20acquired%20land%20through%20compulsory%20purchase%20at%20the%20prevailing%20price%20before%20the%20new%20transport%20route%20was%20announced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDevelopers%20submit%20bids%20to%20acquire%20the%20rights%20to%20develop%20mixed%20use%20commercial%20and%20residential%20buildings%20around%20the%20new%20metro%20stations.%20This%20policy%20was%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20the%20skyscrapers%20that%20form%20the%20iconic%20Hong%20Kong%20skyline.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20revenue%20earned%20by%20the%20city%20from%20this%20%E2%80%98land%20value%20capture%E2%80%99%20has%20been%20enough%20to%20fully%20fund%20the%20construction%20of%20new%20metro%20lines.%20By%20way%20of%20contrast%2C%20most%20cities%20with%20a%20metro%20rely%20on%20huge%20capital%20grants%20from%20the%20municipality%20or%20national%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20the%20urban%20development%20ministry%20publishes%20workable%20plans%20to%20retrofit%20TOD%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20haphazard%20city%20zoning%20and%20on-going%20plans%20to%20build%20metros%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%20In%20China%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20less%20inhibited%20about%20compulsorily%20acquiring%20land%20and%20funnelling%20the%20profits%20from%20rezoning%20into%20public%20goods.%20The%20tradition%20in%20India%20isn%E2%80%99t%20so%20communitarian.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEnergy%20policy%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20does%20not%20say%20much%20about%20energy%20policy%20and%20expenditure%20signalling%20continuity%20with%20its%20pre-election%20policy.%20Back%20in%202022%2C%20India%20updated%20its%20%E2%80%9Cnationally-determined%20contributions%E2%80%9D%20(international%20commitments%20under%20the%20Paris%20climate%20agreement)%20and%20has%20a%20set%20of%20energy%20policies%20to%20deliver%20on%20the%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProgress%20is%20being%20made%20increasing%20generation%20capacity%20to%2050%25%20which%20is%20projected%20to%20be%20met%20by%20zero-carbon%20electricity%20by%202030.%20In%20support%20of%20the%20Make%20in%20India%20objective%2C%20customs%20duty%20is%20being%20abolished%20for%20goods%20involved%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309007%2Fprof-ravindra-gettu-iit-madras-scientists-recycle-waste-concrete-using-solar-thermal-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20manufacture%20of%20solar%20cells%20and%20panels%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20stimulate%20assembling%20of%20such%20parts%20locally%20and%20will%20also%20marginally%20reduce%20the%20price%20of%20solar%20PV%20installations.%20The%20funding%20for%20the%20PM-Surya%20Ghar%20scheme%20supporting%20the%20installation%20of%20a%20crore%20solar%20PV%20homes%20was%20held%20at%20Rs%2075%2C021%20crore.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20announced%20funding%20for%20a%20new%20800%20MW%20thermal%20power%20plant%20operated%20as%20a%20NTPC-BHEL%20joint%20venture%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20push%20for%20sustainable%20initiatives%2C%20this%20funding%20will%20use%20ultra-super%20critical%20coal%20technology%2C%20which%20despite%20being%20less%20carbon%20intensive%20than%20the%20older%20technology%2C%20will%20remain%20a%20major%20source%20of%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGreen%20taxonomy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20energy%20transition%20needs%20huge%20and%20sustained%20investment%20in%20green%20infrastructure.%20The%20sums%20are%20so%20large%20and%20the%20threats%20so%20near%20that%20international%20climate%20finance%20needs%20to%20supplement%20local%20funding%20sources.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20announced%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20intention%20to%20produce%20a%20taxonomy%20for%20climate%20finance%20to%20classify%20legitimate%20green%20projects%20and%20call-out%20the%20greenwash.%20The%20EU%20commission%20and%20the%20Chinese%20financial%20regulators%20pioneered%20the%20publication%20of%20green%20taxonomies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20creation%20of%20a%20taxonomy%20will%20take%20time%2C%20and%20there%20might%20be%20merit%20in%20India%20simply%20copying%20either%20the%20EU%E2%80%99s%20or%20the%20Chinese%20model%20with%20minimal%20changes.%20Their%20development%20involves%20technical%20experts%20systematically%20looking%20at%20different%20economic%20branches%2C%20like%20agriculture%20or%20electricity%20generation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20specify%20which%20activities%20qualify%20as%20%E2%80%98green%E2%80%99%20investments%20that%20make%20a%20meaningful%20contribution%20to%20our%20environmental%20challenges%2C%20and%20which%20do%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20EU%20taxonomy%20wind%20and%20solar%20power%20generation%2C%20the%20manufacture%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F283038%2Fbengaluru-startup-micelio-mobility-invests-crores-india-ev-infrastructure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epurchase%20of%20EV%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%20qualify%20while%20the%20use%20of%20gas%20or%20coal%20%E2%80%94%20even%20ultra-super%20critical%20coal%20and%20hybrid%20transport%20vehicles%20%E2%80%94%20do%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%E2%80%99s%20taxonomy%20is%20aligned%20to%20the%20international%20norms%2C%20it%20should%20help%20international%20green%20investors%20quickly%20sift%20through%20projects%2C%20funds%20and%20debt%20instruments%20certified%20with%20the%20Indian%20taxonomy%20that%20meet%20their%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202017%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298273%2Fsebi-consultation-paper-green-debt-securities-invest-in-sustainable-finance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20published%20and%20updated%20green%20debt%20guidelines%20that%20ensure%20promoters%20of%20green%20financial%20products%2C%20explaining%20exactly%20how%20investors%E2%80%99%20money%20would%20be%20spent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20guidelines%20provided%20transparency%2C%20they%20gave%20a%20lot%20of%20wiggle%20room%20for%20%E2%80%98mildly%E2%80%99%20green%20projects%20to%20be%20funded%20even%20if%20they%20are%20not%20green%20enough%20to%20contribute%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20climate%20or%20biodiversity%20goals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taxonomy%20will%20hopefully%20set%20tough%20green%20standards%20that%20ensure%20the%20investment%20progresses%20India%E2%80%99s%20Nationally%20Determined%20Contribution%20(NDC).%20When%20the%20taxonomy%20is%20published%2C%20we%20should%20check%20to%20ensure%20that%20fossil%20fuel%20generation%20and%20non-organic%20agriculture%20are%20excluded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20taxonomy%20could%20also%20be%20applied%20to%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(RBI)%20green%20bank%20deposits%2C%20thus%20ensuring%20savers%20funds%20only%20lent%20for%20genuinely%20green%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20first%20budget%20for%20the%20current%20coalition%20government%20has%20made%20incremental%20progress%20on%20old%20themes%20like%20solar%20power%20generation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F196917%2Fgujarat-farmer-zero-budget-natural-farming-double-income-organic-vegetables-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20opens%20up%20planning%20and%20discussion%20of%20game-changing%20new%20ideas%20in%20urban%20development%2Fpublic%20transport%20and%20green%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20written%20by%20Prashant%20Vaze%20who%20is%20a%20Goa-based%20writer%20and%20environmental%20economist.%20He%20spent%20most%20of%20his%20career%20in%20the%20UK%20civil%20service%2C%20but%20now%20focuses%20on%20climate%20finance%20issues.%20He%20has%20published%20a%20number%20of%20climate%20fiction%20short-stories%20and%20technical%20articles%20on%20climate%2C%20the%20energy%20transition%20and%20finance.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EUnion%20Budget%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiabudget.gov.in%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edocuments%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%202024-25.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EZero%20budget%20natural%20farming%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvikaspedia.in%2Fagriculture%2Fbest-practices%2Fsustainable-agriculture%2Fclimate-smart-agriculture%2Fzero-budget-natural-farming-in-andhra-pradesh%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVikaspedia.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.a