2Fskynews-steven-van-de-velde_6592869.jpg%3F20240627204840%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-is-steven-van-de-velde-the-dutch-child-rapist-playing-beach-volleyball-at-the-olympics-13186670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20start%20of%20the%20Olympics%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20the%20controversial%20appearance%20of%20a%20child%20rapist%20on%20the%20beach%20volleyball%20court.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A112%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-is-steven-van-de-velde-the-dutch-child-rapist-playing-beach-volleyball-at-the-olympics-13186670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-is-steven-van-de-velde-the-dutch-child-rapist-playing-beach-volleyball-at-the-olympics-13186670%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwho-is-steven-van-de-velde-the-dutch-child-rapist-playing-beach-volleyball-at-the-olympics-13186670%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Started%20With%20Few%20Jars%20on%20The%20Roadside%2C%20How%20a%20Homemaker%20Built%20Her%20Pickle%20Empire%20Earning%20Rs%205%20Crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%202014%2C%20Krishna%20Yadav%20stood%20before%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%2C%20holding%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20for%20Diversified%20Agriculture.%20Her%20entire%20life%20journey%20flashed%20before%20her%20eyes%20as%20she%20gazed%20at%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20the%20small%20village%20of%20Daulatpur%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Krishna%20never%20attended%20school.%20After%20her%20marriage%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Bulandshahr%2C%20where%20she%20faced%20a%20dire%20situation%20when%20her%20husband%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20traffic%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLater%2C%20he%20tried%20to%20start%20a%20vehicle%20trading%20business%2C%20but%20we%20incurred%20huge%20losses.%20We%20had%20to%20sell%20our%20two%20houses%2C%20each%20spread%20across%20150%20%3Cem%3Egaj%20%3C%2Fem%3E(approximately%201%2C300%20sqft).%20It%20became%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20us%20to%20survive.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20eat%20vegetables%20anymore%20and%20survived%20on%20%3Cem%3Enamak%20roti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(salt%20and%20flatbread)%20for%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20decided%20to%20move%20to%20Delhi%20to%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20search%20of%20work.%20With%20only%20Rs%20500%20in%20her%20pocket%2C%20she%20relocated%20to%20the%20city%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20their%20three%20young%20children.%20%E2%80%9CI%20looked%20for%20jobs%2C%20but%20without%20any%20formal%20education%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20work.%20My%20husband%20also%20struggled%20to%20find%20employment.%20After%20two%20months%2C%20we%20began%20working%20on%20a%20field%20through%20sharecropping%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharecropping%20is%20a%20legal%20arrangement%20where%20a%20landowner%20permits%20a%20tenant%20to%20cultivate%20their%20land%2C%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20crops%20produced.%20The%20five-member%20family%20began%20living%20in%20a%20small%20room%20on%20the%20field.%20They%20spent%20their%20days%20cultivating%20vegetables%2C%20but%20the%20income%20from%20their%20efforts%20was%20insufficient%20to%20sustain%20them.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20price%20of%20vegetables%20in%20the%20market%20would%20fluctuate%20and%20we%20would%20hardly%20earn%20any%20profits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Starting%20with%20karonda%20(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358852%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20Krishna%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20life%20when%20she%20heard%20about%20a%20training%20programme%20on%20value%20addition%20of%20post-harvest%20losses%20through%20a%20television%20programme.%20She%20enrolled%20in%20a%20course%20at%20Krishi%20Vigyan%20Kendra%20(KVK)%2C%20where%20she%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAmit%2520tells%2520The%2520Better%2520India%2Ctastes%2520it%2520becomes%2520a%2520fan.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emastered%20the%20art%20and%20science%20of%20making%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurabba%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marmalade).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20new%20path%20for%20her%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20Rs%20500%20to%20Rs%205%20crore%20empire%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20an%20enthused%20student%2C%20Krishna%20would%20set%20out%20to%20the%20training%20centre%20with%20post-harvest%20losses%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%20from%20her%20field%2C%20a%20few%20spices%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20utensils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlthough%20I%20grew%20up%20seeing%20my%20%3Cem%3Edadi%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Enani%20%3C%2Fem%3E(grandmothers)%20make%20pickles%2C%20the%20know-how%20that%20I%20learnt%20in%20the%20training%20was%20insightful.%20As%20homemakers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20calculate%20the%20amounts%20of%20spices%20and%20salt%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20pickle.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20ways%20to%20enhance%20the%20taste%20as%20well%20as%20the%20shelf%20life%20of%20pickles%20naturally.%20The%20key%20was%20the%20measurement%20of%20spices%20and%20oils%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Krishna%20started%20making%20the%20pickles%2C%20but%20she%20had%20little%20knowledge%20of%20commercialising%20the%20products.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20set%20up%20a%20small%20table%20on%20the%20roadside%20and%20put%20our%20products%20on%20display.%20It%20was%20not%20a%20very%20busy%20road%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20attract%20people%20to%20our%20stall.%20So%2C%20we%20placed%20two%20large%20earthen%20pots%20of%20water%20along%20with%20the%20pickles.%20I%20offered%20pickles%20as%20samples%20to%20those%20who%20stopped%20to%20drink%20free%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20simple%20yet%20effective%20strategy%20slowly%20built%20her%20customer%20base.%20She%20also%20started%20participating%20in%20local%20fairs%20to%20promote%20the%20products.%20Over%20the%20next%20few%20years%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20her%20pickles%20grew%2C%20allowing%20her%20to%20formally%20launch%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20eventually%20open%20her%20own%20factory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarting%20with%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(black%20currants)%2C%20she%20introduced%20a%20variety%20of%20pickles%2C%20including%20mangoes%2C%20chillies%2C%20and%20lemons.%20Today%2C%20she%20offers%20over%20250%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300822%2Fsenior-citizen-entrepreneur-sheila-pickles-jams-traditional-kerala-recipes-home-business-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evarieties%20of%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20herbal%20juices%2C%20chutneys%2C%20marmalades%2C%20and%20syrups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Krishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-1-1722235329-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358853%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKrishna%20was%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Farmer%20Award%20in%202014.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Rohilla%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20for%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20pickles%20perfectly%20capture%20the%20essence%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353263%2Fphilos-pickles-kerala-delivery-india-how-to-start-a-homemade-pickle-business-tips-tincy-thomas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehomemade%20goodness%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20offering%20a%20nostalgic%20taste.%20Their%20wide%20variety%20of%20flavours%20caters%20to%20every%20palate%20and%20mood.%20Whenever%20I%20open%20one%20of%20their%20jars%2C%20it%20bursts%20with%20authentic%20tastes%20and%20aromas%2C%20enhancing%20my%20simple%20meals.%20These%20pickles%20never%20disappoint%2C%20consistently%20maintaining%20their%20taste%20and%20quality%20over%20the%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishna%20has%20established%20a%20five-storey%20facility%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20she%20manufactures%2010%20to%2020%20quintals%20of%20pickles%20daily%2C%20and%20her%20company%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20annual%20turnover%20of%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20her%20extraordinary%20determination%20and%20entrepreneurial%20spirit%2C%20she%20has%20been%20recognised%20with%20multiple%20awards%20including%20the%20Outstanding%20Women%20Award%20from%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20on%20the%20occasion%20of%20International%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Day%202012%3B%20the%20Innovative%20Award%20for%20Agriculture%20and%20allied%20activities%20during%20the%20Global%20Agriculture%20Summit%202013%3B%20and%20the%20prestigious%20N%20G%20Ranga%20Award%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20a%20homemaker%20and%20my%20core%20job%20was%20to%20look%20after%20the%20household%20duties.%20But%20I%20wanted%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20family%20income%20in%20our%20dire%20times.%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20let%20my%20children%20face%20the%20brunt%20of%20our%20financial%20crisis.%20It%20was%20a%20small%20step%2C%20and%20I%20never%20imagined%20I%20would%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%20She%20adds%20that%20her%20husband%20and%20eldest%20son%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20business%2C%20while%20her%20other%20two%20children%20are%20currently%20pursuing%20their%20higher%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20I%20have%20both%20%3Cem%3Egaadi%20bangla%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20car%20and%20a%20bungalow)%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20dignity%20to%20walk%20with%20pride.%20As%20a%20child%2C%20I%20aspired%20to%20be%20on%20television%2C%20and%20that%20dream%20came%20true%20with%20my%20business.%20However%2C%20achieving%20this%20success%20required%20consistent%20hard%20work.%20If%20I%20were%20to%20stop%20now%2C%20I%20would%20risk%20losing%20everything%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20example%2C%20Krishna%20emphasises%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20adversity%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20resilience.%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20be%20bogged%20down%20by%20failures.%20Do%20not%20view%20helplessness%20or%20failure%20as%20a%20setback%20but%20as%20a%20stepping%20stone%20to%20greater%20achievements.%20If%20one%20door%20closes%2C%20many%20others%20open%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722240366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fpickles-2_11zon-1722235303.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Krishna%20Yadav%20moved%20to%20Delhi%20from%20a%20small%20village%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20She%20began%20selling%20pickles%20on%20the%20roadside.%20Eventually%2C%20she%20established%20%E2%80%98Shri%20Krishna%20Pickles%E2%80%99%2C%20growing%20her%20business%20into%20a%20successful%20enterprise%20with%20over%20250%20varieties%20of%20products%20and%20a%20five-storey%20factory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358846%2Futtar-pradesh-krishna-yadav-pickle-business-delhi-earn-crores-woman-empowerment%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%2