0with%20less%20vegetation%20were%20easily%20inundated%2C%20Biswas%20saw%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352436%2Fmangrove-plantation-sundarbans-afforestation-conservation-south-parganas-west-bengal-cyclone-blind-activist%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emangroves%20as%20the%20only%20hope%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20region.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20shrubs%20act%20as%20a%20natural%20barrier%20against%20flooding%20and%20waves%20during%20cyclones%2C%20he%20notes.%20In%202005%2C%20he%20started%20to%20plant%20mangroves%20along%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20Bidyadhari%20River%20and%20was%20soon%20joined%20by%20the%20local%20women.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20confident%20of%20their%20approach%2C%20it%20was%20in%20May%202021%20that%20they%20saw%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20efforts%20when%20Cyclone%20Yaas%20hit%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20cyclone%5D%20inundated%20several%20coastal%20villages%20in%20the%20Sundarbans.%20However%2C%20it%20failed%20to%20breach%20the%20river%20banks%20nor%20did%20it%20render%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20Jharkhali%20homeless%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20low-lying%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%20Bijay%20Kumar%20Kabi%2C%20director%20at%20Action%20for%20Protection%20of%20Wild%20Animals%20in%20Odisha%20planted%20a%20mangrove%20forest%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fmangrove-plantation-3-1721985669.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F