0or%20settling%20abroad%2C%20the%2032-year-old%20was%20sitting%20in%20her%20tiny%20room%20surrounded%20by%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-3-1721879414.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kajal%20says%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20relate%20to%20the%20previous%20version%20of%20herself%20anymore.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-3-1721879414.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-3-1721879414-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-3-1721879414-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-3-1721879414-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FKajal-3-1721879414-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358415%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKajal%20says%20she%20can%E2%80%99t%20relate%20to%20the%20previous%20version%20of%20herself%20anymore.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20she%20went%20on%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20prelims%20exams%20but%20a%20tragedy%20struck.%20%E2%80%9CA%20day%20before%20the%20prelims%2C%20I%20experienced%20a%20severe%20stomach%20ache.%20The%20doctor%20advised%20immediate%20surgery%20for%20appendicitis.%20I%20requested%20him%20to%20give%20me%20some%20pain%20relief%20so%20that%20at%20least%20I%20could%20appear%20for%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20going%20to%20the%20centre%2C%20Kajal%20fainted%20and%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital.%20The%20surgery%20was%20performed%20on%20the%20day%20of%20her%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%